column3: Departure hall ke center mein "Information" likha hua counter hai.

column2: Main ne online check-in kiya hai, lekin seat number nahi mila.
column3: Iska matlab hai seat aapko counter pe hi assign ki jayegi.

column2: Kya check-in staff se window seat request kar sakta hoon?
column3: Haan, agar available ho to wo zaroor de dete hain.

column2: Check-in ke baad duty-free shop tak jane mein kitna time lagta hai?
column3: Immigration ke baad 5-10 minute lagte hain.

column2: Kya expired passport pe domestic travel kar sakte hain?
column3: Nahi, travel ke liye valid ID zaroori hai. Expired passport nahi chalega.

column2: Mere bag pe "Heavy" ka tag kyun lagaya hai?
column3: Agar bag 15kg se zyada ho to handling staff ki aasani ke liye ye tag lagaya jata hai.

column2: Kya check-in ke liye mobile battery full honi chahiye?
column3: Haan, behtar hai ke full ho taake aap E-ticket aaram se dikha sakein.

column2: Agar main apne bag ka weight kam karna chahoon, to samaan kahan rakhun?
column3: Airport pe aisi koi facility nahi hai, aapko samaan kisi ko dena hoga ya dispose karna hoga.

column2: Kya airport staff baggage wrapping mein madad karta hai?
column3: Nahi, iske liye alag service counter hota hai jahan payment karni hoti hai.

column2: Boarding pass milne ke baad seedha gate pe jana hota hai?
column3: Nahi, pehle immigration aur security check hota hai, uske baad gate pe jate hain.
